{"tid":1430294,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍取代警察 警察將失業","createTime":"2019-08-07T16:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T04:42:06.000Z","uid":158832,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f3ea620c1218474d1800e64ca32ae1f8e38ac132","tid":1430294,"uid":158832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:57:51.000Z","msg":"(已證實) 解放軍混入左防暴警察 所以政府一直唔成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418512\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418512</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有證據顯示有解放軍混入防暴警察<br />\n<br />\n據一個駐港解放軍據顯示月薪只有數百元<br />\n而警察散仔底薪都兩萬幾千，加上OT郁下都幾萬銀一個月<br />\n<br />\n考慮到維穩費，實在冇必要長期動用香港警察<br />\n因為相比解放軍，警察實在係貴而不實<br />\n比幾萬蚊警察，我唔請10個老解返黎撳住香港人打？<br />\n<br />\n不如留返香港d錢黎打貿易戰仲實際啦，做咩要益班低學歷香港人呢？<br />\n所以我斷言，中共如果要加強香港管治<br />\n香港警察一定冇得撈，遲早失業，恭喜恭喜"},{"pid":"09d8e1175d5d04e99766a944a92cb8090f1f0eb7","tid":1430294,"uid":2562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:58:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L17OqaU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL17OqaU.jpg&h=8e4952ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tcqHuCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtcqHuCA.jpg&h=d468b84a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZJ8NFKg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZJ8NFKg.jpg&h=a40663df&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pinuT4g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpinuT4g.jpg&h=61ad88c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"020574b0afb058a4f946a6c60b546035b279d0f6","tid":1430294,"uid":158832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:00:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>(已證實) 解放軍混入左防暴警察 所以政府一直唔成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418512\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418512</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有證據顯示有解放軍混入防暴警察<br />\n<br />\n<d